
{Style.UNDERLINE}{Style.BRIGHT}Name{Style.RESET_ALL}{Style.END}:
  Send text

{Style.UNDERLINE}{Style.BRIGHT}Usage{Style.RESET_ALL}{Style.END}:
  sendtext [OPTIONS] target

{Style.UNDERLINE}{Style.BRIGHT}Options{Style.RESET_ALL}{Style.END}:
  <target>              Target to send message.
  -f --file <filename>  Messages file.
  -c --count <count>    Count of messages.
  -h --help             Show this help message.
  -v --version          Show program's version number.

